Multicore (Parallel) Bundle Adjustment
--------------------------------------

http://grail.cs.washington.edu/projects/mcba/

I found this on the web after noticing bundle adjustment in OpenCV takes forever
when panoramas have many many cameras (images). In OpenCV it is a serial CPU
code and often consumes the majority of execution time.

Image data sets are provided by this other project:
    Bundle Adjustment in the Large
    http://grail.cs.washington.edu/projects/bal/

